<td valign="top" style="padding:4px 10px;">Any method involving the notion of <b>entropy</b>, the very existence of which depends on the <a href="/wiki/Second_law_of_thermodynamics" title="Second law of thermodynamics">second law of thermodynamics</a>, will doubtless seem to many far-fetched, and may repel beginners as obscure and difficult of comprehension.</td>
<td width="20" valign="bottom" style="color:#B2B7F2;font-size:36px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif;font-weight:bold;text-align:right;padding:10px 10px;">”</td>
